{"tid":945832,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"啲人過馬路可唔以唔好掛住睇電話","createTime":"2018-12-18T07:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T08:09:44.000Z","uid":216662,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1cf3b4235d33d08ea24b1c06445e2955d4275e","tid":945832,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"啱啱過馬路有一大一細，兩個都掛住望電話，個細路大概10歲8歲，紅燈緊望都唔望就行咗出去，我見到就衝出去捉住細路條頸帶咗佢去對面，佢老母先知個仔幾乎俾的士撞大聲叫咗出嚟，之後我就鬧爆佢老母，話佢出街過馬路都唔拖住個仔點做人老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行街打機嗰啲又係，打機唔該就行埋一邊企，咪阻住條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知以為你幾百萬上落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ef4c2adb33f65a9f1b2d4fa334094686147cd8","tid":945832,"uid":126507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"是但啦，撞我兩下又唔使死嘅"},{"pid":"d8518ec39f74f2119cdbc6e27b753a53579f38dd","tid":945832,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:40:34.000Z","msg":"因為我係大人囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12addc2ad15b7486d567099b74adfa957c51c3c2","tid":945832,"uid":216662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66ef4c2adb33f65a9f1b2d4fa334094686147cd8","tid":945832,"uid":126507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:39:05.000Z","msg":"是但啦，撞我兩下又唔使死嘅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"撞到人地要坐監嗰下慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f59a5b7054e65e73419f56681d778939c61b753","tid":945832,"uid":3695,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"我早幾年如果唔係㩒住電話過馬路行慢咗嘅話<br />\n一早就比個衝紅燈嘅南亞佬車死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f71f5d1f8f9976201